                        <p>You can also look into encrypted network and sniff multicast traffic trying to detect used network protocols and services.</p>
                        <p>In case of WPA/WPA2 handshakes will be found in analyzed pcap file you can view and download them as .hccapx file to try to recover password with Hashcat.</p>
