                    <div class="col-sm-6 align-self-center">
                        <h3>DNS queries investigation</h3>
                        <p>You can explore all name resolution protocols like classic DNS, mDNS (Multicast DNS) and NBNS (NetBIOS Name Service) to gather information about network structure and activity of running services.</p>
                        <p>Filters allow separate DNS traffic by type and analyze queried names, targert servers or multicast/broadcast addresses (in case of mDNS and NBNS).</p>
                    </div>
